{"tid":962177,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★港人希望指數暴跌35分　全球最悲觀地區排第5","createTime":"2018-12-30T16:22:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T02:27:02.000Z","uid":19454,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"970fae9d232263e2aad76bdc5bd6222acb2edd34","tid":962177,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T16:22:48.000Z","msg":"2019年即將來臨，惜港人對新一年卻不甚樂觀。國際民意調查機構「蓋洛普(GALLUP INTERNATIONAL ASSOCIATION)」向全球51個國家或地區進行「希望指數(Hope Index)」調查，香港由去年的正10分急跌至負25分，跌幅達35分，成為全球最悲觀地區的第5位。<br />\n<br />\n調查受訪者達5萬人，當中500人為香港人。當被問道「你認為2019年會比2018年更好、更差或是一樣？」覺得將會更差的香港受訪者由去年的22%升至45%，而覺得會更好的受訪況者由32%跌至22%。希望指數<span style=\"color: red;\">最低的國家依次為中東國家約旦(負48分)、黎巴嫩(負42分)、意大利(負40分)及南韓(負30分)</span>，而香港則以負25分排行第5。<br />\n<br />\n調查中亦問到會否認為2019年世界會變得較和平，高達67%受訪港人認為世界會變得較為混亂(troubled)，只有7%人認為會變得較和平，總分數為負60，成為全球各國中對世界和平感到最悲觀的第2位，只稍高於負64分的法國。<br />\n<br />\n該調查機構主席Kancho Stoychev表示，調查結果反映愈富有的國家對來年愈悲觀，「與無法擁有相比，人們對失去的恐懼更大(the fear of losing what you have is bigger than the fear not to have)」，而歐洲地區近年愈見悲觀，美國近10年則持續對未來抱樂觀態度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181230/bkn-20181230214758663-1230_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181230%2Fbkn-20181230214758663-1230_00822_001.html&d=hm2g6INAMOabbn7Boy1dYcP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=1af8a570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181230/bkn-20181230214758663-1230_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2b95f8570ec5cda58a56266b9e631b1337e35b2f","tid":962177,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T16:23:38.000Z","msg":"香港都唔係包尾 都唔係好差啫 仲有4個國家差過香港喎"},{"pid":"34199190e295cf27cc39870aeab391d41ca2764d","tid":962177,"uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T16:24:14.000Z","msg":"1 約旦(負48分)、<br />\n2 黎巴嫩(負42分)、<br />\n3 意大利(負40分)<br />\n4 南韓(負30分)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">5 香港</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3e09401b9c1a4c74852cf1d5863883baa08cc6fa","tid":962177,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T16:37:36.000Z","msg":"HK no IT"},{"pid":"55f17ea1ed73d8eede43785130022ca8125e329f","tid":962177,"uid":122,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T16:47:26.000Z","msg":"無前景可言<br />\n生存、無生活"},{"pid":"b45b2c69fe67570e6c9646f5ac2d354a292ccaa8","tid":962177,"uid":46245,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T16:57:24.000Z","msg":"反而想知點解南韓咁低？"},{"pid":"fc179d93bee87e738da7b738ae5a35edd00a843d","tid":962177,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T17:01:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c2a2e7cbf61b4be23099024831d280b960bb0e9","tid":962177,"uid":11148,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b45b2c69fe67570e6c9646f5ac2d354a292ccaa8","tid":962177,"uid":46245,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T16:57:24.000Z","msg":"反而想知點解南韓咁低？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T17:04:03.000Z","msg":"亞洲第一地獄鬼國<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"365b795bdb46bd3ed7d5f5e7dda49d2d6654cdc2","tid":962177,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T17:05:30.000Z","msg":"反而想知意大利點解咁悲觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97291ca7a583eb3686b42610c44f11b3ad7b0525","tid":962177,"uid":160807,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9c2a2e7cbf61b4be23099024831d280b960bb0e9","tid":962177,"uid":11148,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b45b2c69fe67570e6c9646f5ac2d354a292ccaa8","tid":962177,"uid":46245,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T16:57:24.000Z","msg":"反而想知點解南韓咁低？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T17:04:03.000Z","msg":"亞洲第一地獄鬼國<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cit